Presents information by presenting event info to the screen

Main file of the program; run this file to run the entire program

How Users or any type are able to login into the app.

Room

RoomManager
A Use Case class that manages the functionality of room.

A class that allow Users to sign up/cancel spot for an event
Speaker

is an abstract class that contains basic information every user of this program should have
